OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FExperts question Sunak's   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'maths until 18' plan      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The prime minister's idea for all      
OL,6, pupils in England to study some form of
OL,7, maths up until the age of 18 would be  
OL,8, challenging to implement, experts say. 
OL,10,FA panel of specialists told the        
OL,11,FEducation select committee they broadly
OL,12,Fsupport the "worthy ambition".         
OL,14,FHowever, a lack of maths teachers and a
OL,15,Ffocus on exams meant "fundamental      
OL,16,Freform" would be needed, they said.    
OL,18,FIt comes after Rishi Sunak said the UK 
OL,19,Fmust "reimagine our approach to        
OL,20,Fnumeracy".                             
